<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 18 日星期四 01:51:28 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[8,000-Year-Old Architectural Plans Discovered in Jordan & Saudi Arabia]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110430013" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429445_0:0:465:641_1440x900_80_0_1_234a5644e6d511ed38692153030b9d29.png?source-sid=cc_by_40" data-photoview-image-id="1110429427" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/8000-year-old-architectural-plans-discovered-in-jordan--saudi-arabia-1110430013.html?share-img=1110429427"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" title="抄送 4.0">CC BY 4.0</a> / © 2023 Crassard 等人。 / <a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0277927" title="最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。">最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">在 JKSH F15 遗址发现时雕刻的石头的照片（整块巨石被发现是躺着的，为了拍照而垂直放置）。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_by_40" alt="Photograph of the engraved stone at the time of discovery at the JKSH F15 site (the monolith was found lying down and was set vertically for the photograph). - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="在 JKSH F15 遗址发现时雕刻的石头的照片（整块巨石被发现是躺着的，为了拍照而垂直放置）。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429445_0:190:465:452_1920x0_80_0_0_b360700b8cea30a711475b97488d3f77.png" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429445_0:190:465:452_640x0_80_0_0_70f69df2ee8fbca255b7baf7f3c84e89.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429445_0:190:465:452_1280x0_80_0_0_b7c1cb51d25a368e8a6439eb14469951.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429445_0:190:465:452_1920x0_80_0_0_b360700b8cea30a711475b97488d3f77.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" title="抄送 4.0">CC BY 4.0</a> / © 2023 Crassard 等人。 / <a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0277927" title="最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。">最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。</a> </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶戈尔·沙波瓦洛夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_shapovalov_egor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a><a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.shapovalov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">欧洲和阿拉伯考古学家在约旦和沙特阿拉伯发现了两份古代建筑图，它们是 8,000 至 9,000 年前中东古代居民在岩石上绘制的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由里昂大学首席研究员雷米·克拉萨德 (Rémy Crassard) 领导的阿拉伯和欧洲考古学家团队发现了被认为是高度发达文明建筑计划最古老的例子之一。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “然而，尽管数千年来人类建筑改变了自然空间及其周围环境，但很少有此类人造建筑的计划或地图早于美索不达米亚和古埃及有文字文明的原始历史时期，”官员在其中的调查结果中写道。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110430013" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/8000-year-old-architectural-plans-discovered-in-jordan--saudi-arabia-1110430013.html?share-block=1110430015" data-title="&amp;quot;However, while human constructions have modified natural spaces and their surroundings for many millennia, few plans or maps of such human-made structures predate the protohistoric period of the literate civilizations of Mesopotamia and Ancient Egypt,&amp;quot; officials wrote in there findings."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>官员们在他们的研究中详细说明了“迄今为止最古老的现实计划的特殊发现，刻在石头上，其中一些是来自约旦东南部和沙特阿拉伯北部的人造考古巨型陷阱，其中最古老的可追溯到 9000 年前。”</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">研究人员在检查几个古老的“沙漠风筝”时发现了这一发现，这是由石器时代的狩猎采集部落建造的巨大的类似陷阱的围栏，用于捕获和屠宰大量迁徙或成群移动的动物。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">近几十年来，考古学家在叙利亚、约旦、沙特阿拉伯和中东其他地方发现了大量此类结构。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110430013" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429854_0:0:1493:803_1440x900_80_0_1_1b40b1947bc55eae6deb0e5c142fc35d.png?source-sid=cc_by_40" data-photoview-image-id="1110429836" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/8000-year-old-architectural-plans-discovered-in-jordan--saudi-arabia-1110430013.html?share-img=1110429836"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" title="抄送 4.0">CC BY 4.0</a> / © 2023 Crassard 等人。 / <a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0277927" title="最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。">最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">在岩石艺术调查中发现的雕刻巨石，从北方看。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="cc_by_40" alt="The engraved boulder as discovered during rock art survey, view from the north. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="在岩石艺术调查中发现的雕刻巨石，从北方看。" class=" lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429854_0:0:1493:803_1920x0_80_0_0_567902afab4d3e2d07e5fa765c4522c6.png" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%221033%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1033" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429854_0:0:1493:803_640x0_80_0_0_279bd642e007deb32b69412a77669ce6.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429854_0:0:1493:803_1280x0_80_0_0_61027d0d36dce1073e962d6057f82870.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110429854_0:0:1493:803_1920x0_80_0_0_567902afab4d3e2d07e5fa765c4522c6.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet="">在岩石艺术调查中发现的雕刻巨石，从北方看。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" title="抄送 4.0">CC BY 4.0</a> / © 2023 Crassard 等人。 / <a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0277927" title="最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。">最古老的计划是扩大人造巨型结构。</a> </div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Crassard 和他的同事最近开始调查在约旦东南部的 Jibal al-Khashabiyeh 古代定居点和沙特阿拉伯北部的 Jebel az-Zilliyat 附近建造的几个这样的动物围栏。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由于在其所在地区发现了拟人化的石碑和其他装饰品，这两个地点都引起了考古学家的注意，表明这些定居点的居民文化发展水平很高。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当科学家们研究这些古代遗址附近时，他们在沙漠风筝旁边发现了两块巨石，上面有非常不寻常的岩石艺术，描绘了成组的线条。当科学家们研究它们的形状并将它们与陷阱的照片进行比较时，Crassard 和他的同事发现这两张照片都是这些结构的精确建筑计划。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">考古学家表示，这些图纸帮助古代建造者在建造“沙漠风筝”时避免了错误，“沙漠风筝”的尺寸太大，无法让眼睛完全掌握整个陷阱结构。 Crassard 和他的同事总结说，考虑到这些石碑的年代，这表明建筑艺术及其所需的抽象思维能力出现的时间比科学家过去假设的要早得多。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据人类学家目前的理解，大约在 4 万年前，我们的祖先开始掌握各种艺术形式，并发明了抽象思维的基础。与此同时，更复杂的抽象艺术形式大概出现在文明黎明之后，在古埃及和美索不达米亚第一个城邦形成期间。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">研究结果发表在<a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0277927" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">PLoS One</a>杂志上。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 01:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/8000-year-old-architectural-plans-discovered-in-jordan--saudi-arabia-1110430013.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/8000-year-old-architectural-plans-discovered-in-jordan--saudi-arabia-1110430013.html<category>超越政治</category><category>科学与技术</category><category>沙特阿拉伯</category><category>约旦</category><category>沙漠</category><category>考古学</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[US Judge Rules Musk Subpoena Can Be Served to Tesla in JPMorgan-Epstein Case]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110429604" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/16/1104530605_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_d9b4ee64cbcf9d15c7373241a4325357.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1104530588" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/us-judge-rules-musk-subpoena-can-be-served-to-tesla-in-jpmorgan-epstein-case-1110429604.html?share-img=1104530588"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Susan Walsh</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Elon Musk 于 2020 年 3 月 9 日在华盛顿举行的卫星会议暨展览会上发表讲话。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Elon Musk speaks at the SATELLITE Conference and Exhibition on March 9, 2020, in Washington. - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 于 2020 年 3 月 9 日在华盛顿举行的卫星会议暨展览会上发表讲话。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/16/1104530605_0:160:3073:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_6a91b6752e7b8405a6afac3c9f9e8038.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/16/1104530605_0:160:3073:1888_640x0_80_0_0_9f22bcab43f82068929e72e9ddbf23af.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/16/1104530605_0:160:3073:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_34ab3bc0b791a27b28b094b52543e0b0.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/16/1104530605_0:160:3073:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_6a91b6752e7b8405a6afac3c9f9e8038.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / 苏珊·沃尔什</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊恩德马蒂诺</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_demartino_ian/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">埃隆马斯克是 Twitter 的所有者、特斯拉的首席执行官和 SpaceX 的首席执行官。最近， </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">纽约南区的一名法官周三裁定，检察官可以向特斯拉发出传票，而不是亲自向埃隆马斯克发出传票。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美属维尔京群岛的律师表示，自 4 月以来，他们一直试图向这位特斯拉首席执行官送达传票，但一直未能找到他。传票将迫使他向法庭作证，并交出与该地区就摩根大通与已故并被定罪的性贩子杰弗里·爱泼斯坦的关系提起诉讼的相关文件。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">臭名昭著的小圣詹姆斯岛，也被称为爱泼斯坦岛，据说大部分性交易都发生在这里，位于美属维尔京群岛的管辖范围内。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当爱泼斯坦被发现死在牢房中时，他正在等待性交易指控的审判。他的死被裁定为自杀。<strong>爱泼斯坦此前曾在 2008 年因向未成年人招揽性行为而被定罪，并且在 1998 年至 2013 年期间是摩根大通的客户。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">律师在法庭文件中表示，他们联系了马斯克在特斯拉的律师，询问他们是否愿意代表马斯克接受这项服务，但没有收到回复。周三的裁决允许他们在未经特斯拉批准的情况下这样做。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美属维尔京群岛指责摩根大通帮助促进爱泼斯坦的未成年人性交易业务，并利用他与富人的关系来增加他们的业务。除了马斯克，其他几位富人也被传唤参与此案，包括谷歌联合创始人拉里佩奇和谢尔盖布林、迪士尼前高管迈克尔奥维茨、凯悦酒店执行主席托马斯普利兹克和亿万富翁房地产大亨莫特祖克曼。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>摩根大通首席执行官杰米戴蒙也将于 5 月 26 日因该案被免职。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">爱泼斯坦的一名据称受害者对银行提起了另一起诉讼，提出了类似的指控。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>诉讼没有指控马斯克有任何不当行为，也没有要求他宣誓作证。相反，它要求他提供他本人、摩根大通和爱泼斯坦之间的所有通信，以及<strong>“所有反映或关于爱泼斯坦参与人口贩运和/或他为商业性交易购买女孩或妇女的文件。”</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">摩根大通否认在此案中有任何不当行为。戴蒙此前对银行与爱泼斯坦有关系表示遗憾，但坚称银行不对爱泼斯坦的行为负责。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">摩根大通也一直将责任归咎于爱泼斯坦的朋友、前高管杰斯·斯塔利。斯特利也否认有任何不当行为。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在 2018 年的一次采访中，爱泼斯坦声称，当特斯拉面临美国证券交易委员会的审查时，他曾为马斯克提供建议。爱泼斯坦在那次采访中还预测，马斯克和特斯拉会否认他曾为他提供过建议。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>在周一的一条推文中，马斯克称传票是“愚蠢的”，并声称，“那个白痴 [Epstein] 从来没有就任何事情向我提出建议。”他还在推文中指出，特斯拉在十年前结束了与摩根大通的业务关系。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">特斯拉的一名代表也否认爱泼斯坦曾为该公司提供过建议。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 00:27:15 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/us-judge-rules-musk-subpoena-can-be-served-to-tesla-in-jpmorgan-epstein-case-1110429604.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/us-judge-rules-musk-subpoena-can-be-served-to-tesla-in-jpmorgan-epstein-case-1110429604.html<category>美洲</category><category>杰弗里·爱泼斯坦</category><category>埃隆·马斯克</category><category>杰米戴蒙</category><category>摩根大通</category><category>特斯拉</category><category>推特</category><category>美属维尔京群岛</category><category>诉讼</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ukraine Conflict Direct Result of Biden Foreign Policy Blunders, Iran Hopes - US Senator]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110430213" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109774004_0:0:3078:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_7d8ff80848d1d6c977f9704f315397e7.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1109773986" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230518/ukraine-conflict-direct-result-of-biden-foreign-policy-blunders-iran-hopes---us-senator-1110430213.html?share-img=1109773986"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / SERGEI SUPINSKY 2022 年 2 月 11 日，</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">乌克兰军人在卡车上装载 FGM-148 标枪，这是美国向乌克兰提供的便携式反坦克导弹，作为军事支持的一部分，该导弹于 2022 年 2 月 11 日在基辅鲍里斯波尔机场交付</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="Ukrainian servicemen load a truck with the FGM-148 Javelin, American man-portable anti-tank missile provided by US to Ukraine as part of a military support, upon its delivery at Kiev's airport Borispol on February 11, 2022 - Sputnik International, 1920, 18.05.2023" title="2022 年 2 月 11 日，乌克兰军人在卡车上装载 FGM-148 标枪，这是美国向乌克兰提供的便携式反坦克导弹，作为军事支持的一部分，该导弹在基辅鲍里斯波尔机场交付时" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109774004_0:159:3078:1890_1920x0_80_0_0_e8db6f48e409982446de9456cae7c880.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109774004_0:159:3078:1890_640x0_80_0_0_be245e71bcce8a89de74fa1fffd6a1bb.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109774004_0:159:3078:1890_1280x0_80_0_0_738e7b597bfc3aea2cc6956ad72d2c01.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/17/1109774004_0:159:3078:1890_1920x0_80_0_0_e8db6f48e409982446de9456cae7c880.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / 谢尔盖·苏宾斯基</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：美国参议员特德克鲁兹周三表示，乌克兰冲突是美国总统乔拜登的外交政策错误及其政府试图与伊朗达成核协议的直接结果。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">克鲁兹在哈德逊研究所发表讲话时说：“我们不必打这场战争，这场战争是由乔·拜登总统的外交政策失误直接引起的。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">克鲁兹还表示，拜登政府正在通过向伊朗提供资金来资助乌克兰冲突的双方。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他补充说，拜登将党派政治置于国家安全之上，未能适当武装乌克兰或解决伊朗与俄罗斯之间的合作问题。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">克鲁兹还批评拜登在俄罗斯北溪 2 号管道的建设问题上表现出“软弱”，该管道在拜登上任后在特朗普政府下暂停后恢复。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位参议员说，早点停止该项目可能会阻止俄罗斯在乌克兰开展特别军事行动。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 18 May 2023 00:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/ukraine-conflict-direct-result-of-biden-foreign-policy-blunders-iran-hopes---us-senator-1110430213.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230518/ukraine-conflict-direct-result-of-biden-foreign-policy-blunders-iran-hopes---us-senator-1110430213.html<category>世界</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>冲突</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Video: Researchers Create First 3D Model of Titanic Wreck]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110427119" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110427613_0:0:1211:676_1440x900_80_0_1_ed49d04adae84b6dc19709e1b82689ad.png?source-sid=" data-photoview-image-id="1110427259" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/video-researchers-create-first-3d-model-of-titanic-wreck-1110427119.html?share-img=1110427259"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://atlanticproductions.tv/productions/back-to-the-titanic/" title="大西洋制作/麦哲伦">ATLANTIC PRODUCTIONS/MAGELLAN</a> / 泰坦尼克号 3D 之旅的截图。</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">泰坦尼克号 3D 之旅的屏幕截图。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="" alt="Screenshot from a 3D tour of the Titanic. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="泰坦尼克号 3D 之旅的屏幕截图。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110427613_4:0:1206:676_1920x0_80_0_0_d2668b70b14ddf96e730904ab763c547.png" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110427613_4:0:1206:676_640x0_80_0_0_cb9b4fb9a5ac0b387086acd137fbee3c.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110427613_4:0:1206:676_1280x0_80_0_0_3fd18ad1e48e718daef653b5ff0f8212.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110427613_4:0:1206:676_1920x0_80_0_0_d2668b70b14ddf96e730904ab763c547.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://atlanticproductions.tv/productions/back-to-the-titanic/" title="大西洋制作/麦哲伦">ATLANTIC PRODUCTIONS/MAGELLAN</a> / 泰坦尼克号 3D 之旅的截图。 </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶戈尔·沙波瓦洛夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_shapovalov_egor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a><a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.shapovalov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">1912 年 4 月 10 日，泰坦尼克号从英国南安普敦启程前往纽约，开始了它的处女航。4 月 14 日晚上，班轮在北大西洋与一座冰山相撞并沉没。至少有 1,400 人因沉船事故丧生。超过 700 名乘客和机组人员设法逃脱。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">新发布的镜头提供了令人惊叹的、前所未见的泰坦尼克号残骸在大西洋底部的景象。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">有史以来第一张泰坦尼克号的全尺寸图像是由 Magellan Ltd 和 Atlantic Productions 的专家创建的，他们将数千张数字图像组合在一起，创建了泰坦尼克号的 3D 重建图。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">数据是通过使用深海潜水器收集的，该潜水器在 2022 年夏季的 200 小时内从不同角度拍摄了 700,000 张照片。官员们表示，由此产生的重建使得能够完整地看到沉船，在从深海潜水器看不到的方式。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">泰坦尼克号新视角！新的扫描揭示了世界上最著名的沉船，这是前所未见的。他们完整地展示了沉船——就好像水已经被排干了……在这里看看<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Titanic?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Titanic</a><br> （镜头： <a href="https://twitter.com/AtlanticProds?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@AtlanticProds</a> / Magellan） <a href="https://t.co/1nOdfc7mWb">pic.twitter.com/1nOdfc7mWb</a></p> - 丽贝卡莫雷尔 (@BBCMorelle) <a href="https://twitter.com/BBCMorelle/status/1658768797270958081?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 17 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">研究人员表示希望研究这些图像能够更好地了解灾难的细节，例如泰坦尼克号撞击海床的确切机制。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “关于这艘船还有一些问题，基本问题需要回答......我们真的不了解与冰山相撞的性质。我们甚至不知道她是否沿着右舷撞了它，正如所有电影中所展示的那样——她可能搁浅在冰山上，”泰坦尼克号分析师帕克斯斯蒂芬森说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110427119" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/video-researchers-create-first-3d-model-of-titanic-wreck-1110427119.html?share-block=1110427122" data-title="&amp;quot;There are still questions, basic questions, that need to be answered about the ship... We really don&amp;#x27;t understand the character of the collision with the iceberg. We don&amp;#x27;t even know if she hit it along the starboard side, as is shown in all the movies - she might have grounded on the iceberg,&amp;quot; said Parks Stephenson, a Titanic analyst."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他还澄清说，外部水下因素正在损坏这艘船，<strong>并强调确定班轮残骸全貌的时间已经不多了</strong>。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “它的深度接近 4,000 米，是一个挑战，而且现场也有水流 - 我们不允许接触任何东西，以免损坏沉船，”来自麦哲伦的 Gerhard Seiffert 说，他带领远征的计划。 “另一个挑战是你必须绘制每一平方厘米的地图——甚至是无趣的部分，比如在碎片场你必须绘制泥浆，但你需要它来填充所有这些有趣的物体之间。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110427119" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/video-researchers-create-first-3d-model-of-titanic-wreck-1110427119.html?share-block=1110427131" data-title="&amp;quot;The depth of it, almost 4,000m, represents a challenge, and you have currents at the site, too - and we&amp;#x27;re not allowed to touch anything so as not to damage the wreck,&amp;quot; said Gerhard Seiffert from Magellan, who led the planning for the expedition. &amp;quot;And the other challenge is that you have to map every square centimetre - even uninteresting parts, like on the debris field you have to map mud, but you need this to fill in between all these interesting objects.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该小组的工作提供了对传奇班轮的规模和更小的细节的更近距离观察，例如其中一个螺旋桨上的序列号、船尾的状态以及这艘注定失败的船只上旅客散落的各种法规和个人物品。图片还提供了对吊艇架甲板的近距离观察，从那里的一个大洞可以瞥见曾经宏伟的楼梯的遗迹。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这艘船的残骸位于距纽芬兰海岸约 350 海里的海床上。泰坦尼克号在沉没过程中一分为二，船头和船尾在海底相距 790 米。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 22:50:33 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/video-researchers-create-first-3d-model-of-titanic-wreck-1110427119.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/video-researchers-create-first-3d-model-of-titanic-wreck-1110427119.html<category>超越政治</category><category>科学与技术</category><category>纽芬兰</category><category>泰坦尼克号</category><category>船残骸</category><category>历史</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ecuadorian President Lasso Dissolves Legislature to Avoid Impeachment]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110428268" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110428068_0:0:3071:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_a5e58398aa6ed7f18cda46c82e191268.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110428050" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/ecuadorian-president-lasso-dissolves-legislature-to-avoid-impeachment-1110428268.html?share-img=1110428050"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Dolores Ochoa</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">警察在厄瓜多尔基多守卫国民议会，2023 年 5 月 17 日，星期三。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Police guard the National Assembly in Quito, Ecuador, Wednesday, May 17, 2023. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="2023 年 5 月 17 日，星期三，警察在厄瓜多尔基多守卫国民议会。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110428068_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_727ab374156cd918838e95cbc896e2b8.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110428068_0:0:3072:1728_640x0_80_0_0_331b50dd1964b73667df4e79099a010e.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110428068_0:0:3072:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_ef86335cc54ad1af296cd823d4247b75.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110428068_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_727ab374156cd918838e95cbc896e2b8.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / 多洛雷斯·奥乔亚</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊恩德马蒂诺</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_demartino_ian/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">解散该国国民议会的法令是在对总统吉列尔莫·拉索 (Guillermo Lasso) 进行弹劾审判的某一天发布的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">厄瓜多尔总统吉列尔莫·拉索于周三通过法令解散了国民议会，一天前，国民议会开始了弹劾审判，似乎有望将他免职。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>该法令于周三早上 7 点宣布。 Lasso 应用厄瓜多尔宪法第 148 条制定了一种称为“交叉死亡”的工具，该工具解散了该国的议会，并要求在 90 天内举行国民议会和总统的新选举。</strong> </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>与此同时，在新议会和可能的新总统就任之前，吉列尔莫将通过法令进行长达六个月的统治。在此期间，对他权力的唯一制衡将是宪法法院，尽管他应该仅限于经济法令。</p><p><strong>选举的获胜者将任职至 2025 年 5 月本届总统和立法任期结束。</strong></p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">国民议会似乎准备以腐败和挪用公款费用为由弹劾吉列尔莫。议员们在周日举行投票，选择议会的权力机构，并展示了反对派联盟的团结，这表明它有足够的票数来弹劾拉索。弹劾他只需要 92 票；在周日的会议上，每项动议都获得了 94 到 100 票，这表明官员们获得了足够的票数来罢免 Lasso。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周二，弹劾审判开始时，拉索出现在议会面前为自己辩护。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “你们是反立法者，”他在国会发言时说。 “我指责你不仅试图降低总统职位的可信度，而且还试图降低民主的可信度。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110428268" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/ecuadorian-president-lasso-dissolves-legislature-to-avoid-impeachment-1110428268.html?share-block=1110428275" data-title="“You are anti-legislators,” he said in a speech on the floor of the National Assembly. “I accuse you of trying not only to take down the credibility of the presidency, but that of democracy.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">对他的弹劾和谴责的投票预计将在本周末进行，但解散议会的法令已经结束了这些程序。拉索此前曾威胁说，如果弹劾继续进行，就会解散该会议厅。它仍然向前发展表明反对派有信心他们将在交叉死亡选举中表现出色。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>对 Lasso 的指控源于国有厄瓜多尔石油舰队 (FLOPEC) 与私有的亚马逊油轮联营公司之间的合同。拉索在辩护中指出，合同是在他上任三年前的 2018 年签署的。他还提到了一份提交给政府监督委员会的不具约束力的报告，该报告认定他没有任何不当行为。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Lasso 进一步声称，他根据主计长办公室的建议对合同进行了调整，他说这使合同对厄瓜多尔更有利可图。然而，反对派声称他对与合同有关的涉嫌挪用公款视而不见，并在明知该交易<strong>“代表国家损失”的情况下继续进行。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">反对派联盟包括仍由厄瓜多尔前总统拉斐尔·科雷亚控制的希望联盟党（UNES）、基督教社会党（PCS）；土着政党 Pachakutik；和社会民主党民主左翼 (ID)。八名独立的国会议员也加入了反对派。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">去年，国民议会弹劾议长瓜达卢佩·洛里，但仅获得81票，不足以弹劾拉索。 Llori 被 Viviana Veloz 取代，后者于周二提出弹劾动议。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一些国会议员表示他们不会接受该法令；然而，军方支持套索。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>厄瓜多尔武装部队司令纳尔逊·普罗亚诺在一份视频声明中指出，该法令符合宪法。多份报告表明，部队关闭了国民议会大楼，并且不允许任何人进入，包括前立法者。</strong> </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>第 148 条允许总统解散国民议会有两个原因：如果国民议会反复无理地阻挠国家发展计划的执行，或者由于严重的政治批评和内部骚乱。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>厄瓜多尔多年来一直在处理经济问题和高犯罪率。作为与国际货币基金组织达成协议的一部分而实施的紧缩措施未能扭转该国的经济困境，并在前厄瓜多尔总统列宁莫雷诺的领导下引发了致命的动荡。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在科雷亚的领导下，厄瓜多尔成为南美洲最安全的国家之一，犯罪率在他执政的最后八年里有所下降，降至他离任以来的最低水平。从那以后，犯罪率每年都在上升，该国 2022 年的谋杀率创下历史新高，每 10 万居民中有 25.5 起凶杀案。这个南美国家有望在 2023 年再次打破纪录。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拉索将犯罪和暴力的增加归咎于贩毒集团。由于暴力事件，他两次宣布一些省份进入紧急状态——一次是在 2021 年 10 月，一次是在 2022 年 4 月。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>科雷亚称解散国民议会的法令是“非法的”，但在一条推文中表示，这是从拉索手中“收复祖国”的机会。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “Lasso 的所作所为是违法的。显然，没有“内乱”。他只是买不到足够多的议员来拯救自己，”他的推文翻译如下。 “无论如何，这是摆脱拉索、他的政府和他租用的议会成员并收复祖国的绝好机会。”</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 21:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/ecuadorian-president-lasso-dissolves-legislature-to-avoid-impeachment-1110428268.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/ecuadorian-president-lasso-dissolves-legislature-to-avoid-impeachment-1110428268.html<category>美洲</category><category>吉列尔莫·拉索</category><category>拉斐尔科雷亚</category><category>列宁·莫雷诺</category><category>厄瓜多尔</category><category>南美洲</category><category>大会</category><category>国会</category><category>政府</category><category>弹劾</category><category>选举</category><category>国民议会</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[US Debt Drama: As Biden Negotiates, Some Suggest He Use Law to Bypass Talks]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110427758" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1c/1109905667_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_88e61039cc8e8baf6bec2fe739993153.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109905649" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-debt-drama-as-biden-negotiates-some-suggest-he-use-law-to-bypass-talks-1110427758.html?share-img=1109905649"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Carolyn Kaster</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">2021 年 6 月 30 日，星期三，在华盛顿的一个雨夜里可以看到白宫。乔·拜登总统将于周五在白宫举行入籍仪式，届时 21 名移民将成为美国公民。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="The White House is seen on a rainy night in Washington, Wednesday, June 30, 2021. President Joe Biden will hold a naturalization ceremony Friday at the White House in which 21 immigrants will become citizens. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="2021 年 6 月 30 日，星期三，在华盛顿的一个雨夜里可以看到白宫。乔·拜登总统将于周五在白宫举行入籍仪式，届时 21 名移民将成为美国公民。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1c/1109905667_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_46020fc46f22f3fce5d9d9fa00e07cec.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1c/1109905667_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_7d8c65989fb00fc1945a9323ff23563b.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1c/1109905667_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_31bb07cfd750553364d6d4ed238728a9.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1c/1109905667_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_46020fc46f22f3fce5d9d9fa00e07cec.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Carolyn Kaster </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：一些政治盟友敦促乔·拜登总统援引美国宪法中的一项法规，以帮助他的政府避免美国支付违约，因为他在国会的竞争对手阻碍提高该国的债务上限，媒体报道周三称。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">第 14 条修正案以前从未使用过，其在此事中的合法性未知。但报道称，拜登所在民主党的一些参议员相信，绕过国会共和党人的反对提高债务上限可能是正确的选择。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">以蒂娜史密斯和伊丽莎白沃伦为首的五位民主党参议员在美国媒体周三公布的给拜登的信件草稿中表示： </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “我们写信紧急请求您准备根据宪法第 14 条修正案行使您的权力，该修正案明确规定：‘美国公共债务的有效性……不应受到质疑。’”使用这一权力将使美国能够继续按时支付账单，而不会拖延，从而防止全球经济灾难。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110427758" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-debt-drama-as-biden-negotiates-some-suggest-he-use-law-to-bypass-talks-1110427758.html?share-block=1110427761" data-title="“We write to urgently request that you prepare to exercise your authority under the 14th Amendment of the Constitution, which clearly states: 'the validity of the public debt of the United States...shall not be questioned.' Using this authority would allow the United States to continue to pay its bills on-time, without delay, preventing a global economic catastrophe.&quot; "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">白宫与共和党就提高债务上限进行了争论，但没有成功，目前债务上限为 31.4 万亿美元。美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，必须在 6 月 1 日之前提高债务上限，以避免债务违约，她说，这将对美国经济和美国人的生计产生不可估量的影响。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>然而，拜登周三对记者表示，他对“有达成 [一项] 协议的途径”持乐观态度。国会共和党领袖、众议院议长凯文麦卡锡周三也表示，他相信美国不会拖欠债务。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，起草致拜登信函的参议员们指出，民主党对债务谈判的某些方面越来越不满，包括共和党要求对获得联邦福利实施更严格的工作要求。 “虽然我们不能拖欠债务，但我们也不能允许破坏性的共和党预算得以实施，”他们说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">民主党人则建议对富人征收更高的税，但共和党人已将其排除在外。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 21:34:24 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/us-debt-drama-as-biden-negotiates-some-suggest-he-use-law-to-bypass-talks-1110427758.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/us-debt-drama-as-biden-negotiates-some-suggest-he-use-law-to-bypass-talks-1110427758.html<category>经济</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>我们</category><category>经济危机</category><category>金融危机</category><category>乔·拜登</category><category>珍妮特·耶伦</category><category>共和党人</category><category>国会</category><category>白色的房子</category></item></channel></rss>